(She is sitting at her desk typing in recipe measurement adjustments to her portfolio with her free hand.)
join marzi (Casual Unsure) left
marzi (Casual Unsure): I thought the hard part was over.
marzi (Casual Worried): I thought the graduation money would be my ticket to my own confectionery.
marzi (Casual Carefree): I just... need a little inspiration first...
leave marzi
