	rosy (Approval): Well at least you seem to be able to take some accountability.
	set {rosy_points} += "5"
	set {al_points} += "5"
if {rosy_points} == 55:
	rosy (Disappointed): ...but it's not really enough.
marzi (Casual Apologetic): ...
rosy (Disappointed): Sweetheart, a flower can't bloom if it doesn't have roots in the dirt.
rosy (Disappointed): We love your passion, but your 'research' drained your entire savings...
rosy (Disappointed): ...and you're going to have to deal with the consequences of your childish decision.
rosy (Disappointed): You've been locked up in your bedroom for months...
rosy: You've been spending more time shopping for sweets, outfits and fidget toys than you have been applying for jobs.
leave rosy
join al (Worry) rightmost
al (Worry): Mom and I agreed on a timeline, Marzi.
al (Worry): You need a steady job.
al (Worry): A real routine.
al (Worry): If you don't have a paying position by the end of the month...
al (Worry): ...we are going to kick you out of the house, Marzipan.
set {panic_points} += "4"
marzi (Casual Very Concerned): !!!
al (Worry): We can't keep funding this chaos.
