madeline (Happy): CANDY!!! I WANT CANDY TOO MARZI!!
leave madeline
join chai (Relaxed) rightmost
chai (Relaxed): Look, if you're going to blow your entire life savings on sugar, you might as well go straight to the source.
chai (Relaxed): Have you been to Starlight City before?
join marzi (Casual Orz) left
marzi (Casual Orz): No...I..I haven't.
marzi (Casual Serious): But that's where the legendary confectionery, The Gilded Macaron is.
marzi (Casual Cowlick): Any confectioner who knows their salt from their sugar knows that...
marzi (Casual Concerned): ...
chai (Exasperated): Well you might not have been searching the job boards...
chai (Relaxed): ...but I have.
chai (Relaxed): There's a new listing for a job opening.
marzi (Casual Amazed): Oh wow! That would be my dream job!
marzi (Casual Worried): B...But what if my portfolio isn't good enough?
marzi (Casual Wingding): What if they don't like me??
marzi (Casual Orz): I'll be living in a tent in the woods!!!
marzi (Casual Orz): ...
marzi (Casual Tears): I DON'T EVEN OWN A TENT!
