chai (Understanding): In through the nose...2...3...4...
chai (Understanding): Hold...2...3...4...
chai (Understanding): Out...2...3...4...
chai (Understanding): Hold...2...3...4...
leave --All--
(Marzi regains her composure as they breathe in rhythm together.)
