join chai (Understanding) rightmost
join marzi (Casual Trust) left
chai (Understanding): They'll like you Marzi.
chai (Understanding): No one has a passion for confectionery arts more intense than you.
chai (Understanding): You've prepared enough, okay?
chai (Love): It's time to put that preparation into action.
join marzi (Casual Confident) left
marzi (Casual Confident): You're right, Chai...
marzi (Casual Confident): I can do this!
leave --All--
(Chai smiles and tosses her a transit card.)
