join marzi (Casual Amazed) left
marzi (Casual Anticipation): Omigosh WOW!
marzi (Casual Anticipation): So this is the legendary Gilded Macaron...
marzi (Casual Love): It's even better than I'd imagined!
marzi (Casual Love): Look at that carousel made of isomalt!
marzi (Casual Amazed): It's so intricate...
marzi (Casual Amazed): I can't wait to make something like that.
marzi (Casual Confident): Okay Marzi, this is it.
marzi (Casual Confident): It's your big chance!
