(Back home the table is set perfectly, though Marzi's side has a few stray sprinkles and a notebook filled with recipes and illustrations of different confections flipped open.)
(Madeline is smashing peas into her highchair tray while Chai tries to distract her with a spoon airplane.)
(Rosy is busy serving sanshoku don to the rest of the family, while Al raises his glass in toast.)
