marzi (Casual Surprised): (Marzi drops her fork, her eyes widen to saucers.)
marzi (Casual Surprised): Wait, really?
marzi (Casual Surprised): You'd really do that?!
marzi (Casual Surprised): I thought you were just going to kick me out high and dry and I'd have to go live in a tent in the woods!
