join rosy (Idle) rightmost
rosy (Idle): Consider it an investment in your roots.
rosy (Idle): All we want is for you to grow and really bloom, Marzi.
rosy (Idle): And you weren't growing all alone up in that attic.
rosy (Idle): We hope having your own "pot" will give you some space to flourish.
rosy (Idle): But remember Marzi-
rosy (Idle): You have to hold this job down to pay the monthly rent.
rosy (Idle): No impulsive quitting...
rosy (Idle): No giving up because it's hard or you're having trouble with a coworker...
rosy (Idle): No blowing your paycheck on imported candy.
marzi (Casual Sweat): (Marzi swallows hard, the crushing weight of Beatrix's cold stare flashing in her mind.)
marzi (Casual Sweat): Right.
marzi (Casual Unsure): Absolutely...
marzi (Casual Unsure): I can be disciplined...
marzi (Casual Unsure): I can be an adult...
marzi (Casual Unsure): (I can be...)
marzi (Casual Unsure): (...normal.)
